    "The methodology is presented in Sect. 3.",
    "In Sect. 4, experimental evaluation is offered.",
    "In Sect. 5, Conclusion and Discussion is provided.",
    "Pre-trained models, trained on large datasets, may have limitations like inability to handle new data types or certain tasks, and may not be optimal for specific tasks due to their training conditions [47] [48] [49] [50].",
